WHO waxay ogaatay khilaafka ka dhexeeya cudurka SARS ee 2002-2004, oo ay u aragtay in dowladda Shiinaha ay si taxadar leh u sameysay oo ay u qaadatay tallaabooyin xakameyn iyo xakameyn ah, iyo cudurkaas oo ay dowladda dhexe "u soo bandhigtay macluumaad ku saabsan saddexda qof ee la soo qabtay ka hor inta aan la bilaabin Sannadka Cusub ee Dayaxa".
Bishii Janaayo 23, si looga jawaabo tallaabooyinka dowladda dhexe ee lagu yareeyo khatarta ka jirta nidaamyada cudurrada Wuhan, taliyaha WHO Gauden Galea ayaa sheegay in "aan jirin wax dareen ah oo ay WHO sameysay", ay tahay "martigelinta ugu muhiimsan ee loo sameeyo si loo xakameeyo cudurka ugu daran" wuxuuna ku baaqay "in aanay jirin wax taariikhda caafimaadka ah". Bishii Janaayo 30, ka dib markii la ogaaday in cudurka uu ka soo baxo qof ilaa qof Shiinaha iyo kororka tirada cudurrada dalalka kale, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday cudurka sida Cudurka Caalamiga ah ee Caalamiga ah (PHEIC), oo ah kii ugu horreeyay ee PHEIC laga soo bilaabo markii la soo saaray cudurka ka dib 2009.
Agaasimaha koowaad ee WHO Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEIC ay tahay sababta oo ah "waxay faafi kartaa adduunka oo dhan, gaar ahaan dalalka ay ka yar yihiin dadka u soo gala iyo kuwa aan haysan nidaam caafimaad oo sax ah.
Iyadoo la jawaabayo hoos u dhaca safarka, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in "la'aanta ay tahay in la xakameeyo nidaamyada caalamiga ah ee safarka iyo ganacsiga" iyo in "WHO ay ku talineyso in la yareeyo ganacsiga ama la yareeyo".
