Ururka Horumarinta Dhaqaalaha ayaa sheegay in ay diyaar u yihiin inay si joogto ah u soo gudbiyaan warbixinno ku saabsan siyaasadda adduunka oo dhan, iyo fikradaha iyo khilaafaadka.
Siyaasadaha loo baahan yahay in la fuliyo nidaamyada caafimaadka iyo ammaanka caalamiga ah si loo yareeyo dhibaatada joogitaanka guriga iyo in la yareeyo safarka, xarunta ayaa ka kooban Siyaasadda Qaranka, iyada oo ujeedadu tahay in la caawiyo waddamada inay bartaan ama ay ku adkeystaan difaaca caalamiga ah ee cudurka faafa ee coronavirus.
Dowladda Shiinaha ayaa waxaa ku baaqday Mareykanka, Wasiirka Xafiiska Wasiirada Ingiriiska Michael Gove, iyo Madaxweynaha Brazil Jair Bolsonaro iyo Eduardo Bolsonaro inay ka hortagaan cudurka faafa ee caalamiga ah, kaasoo ka dhacay gobolka Hubei, ee Shiinaha.
Saraakiisha dowlad goboleedyada qaarkood ee Xisbiga Komunista ee Shiinaha (CPC) ayaa la xiriira inay xakameyn karaan xadgudubyada sharci darada ah ee dadka ee bartamaha Shiinaha, calaamadaha magaalada iyo falcelinta siyaasadeed ee cudurka ee gobollada kale.
Khubarada qaar ayaa aaminsan in munaasabadda ay ka caawineyso in la ilaaliyo qoraaga hore ee Xisbiga Qaramada Midoobay ee Shiinaha Xi Jinping si looga hortago in dadweynaha ay ka hadlaan cudurka Coronavirus.
Madaxda kale ee Shiinaha, sida Zhao Lijan ayaa soo saaray aqoonsigii ugu horreeyay ee ku saabsan cudurka coronavirus ee ka dhashay Wuhan, iyadoo la tixgelinayo habka cudurka COVID-19 ee ka yimid Mareykanka ama Talyaaniga.
Dowladda Mareykanka Donald Trump ayaa coronavirus ugu yeertay "Cudurkii Shiinaha" ama "Cudurkii Wuhan" waxayna sheegtay in Shiinaha uu "u soo bandhigay fayras kale oo hadda ah cudur caalami ah", taas oo sidoo kale ay ku ceebeen qaar ka mid ah dadka soo saaray iyada oo ay ku sheegeen inay tahay waxyeello asal ah iyo "in ay ka xumaato in madaxda dowladdu ay ka hortagaan cudurka".
Daily Beast waxay heshay warbixin ka timid dowladda Mareykanka oo muujineysa nidaamka badbaadada ee ay soo saartay dareenka Nabad Suggida, iyadoo nidaamku uu ku tilmaamay "Wax walba oo ku saabsan Shiinaha.
Waxaa la sheegay in ay tahay in la isku dayo in la arko aragtida wararka si kale, iyadoo la isku darayo in la isugu daro warbaahinta iyo in la soo bandhigo TV-ga. "Waxay soo saareen wargeysyada sida Politico, Foreign Policy, iyo Bloomberg in dhammaan siyaabaha Shiinaha u muuqdaan inay ka caawiyaan Shiinaha ay yihiin kuwo u muuqda inay caalami ahaan u muuqdaan kuwo aan caadi ahayn.
Wasiirka arrimaha dibadda Josep Borrell ayaa sheegay in ay jirto "dhaqdhaqaaqyo deegaan iyo siyaasadeed oo ka dambeeya sidii loo xakameyn lahaa sharafta doorashada iyo "siyaasadda kaalmada".
Borrell ayaa sidoo kale sheegay in "Shiinaha uu si adag u diido warbixintan, marka laga reebo Mareykanka, oo ah shirkad qiimo leh oo lagu kalsoon yahay".
Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ku baaqay Mareykanka inuu ka saaro duulimaadyada ka dhanka ah Suuriya, Venezuela iyo Iran, wuxuuna sidoo kale u dirayaa taageero labadaba ugu dambeeya ee ku qoran.
